---
description: This API returns changed accounts in a specific block number.
---

# eth\_getDiffAccounts

{% hint style="info" %}
Supported on BSC mainnet only.
{% endhint %}

## Parameters

* `blockNumber` - The block number in HEX format.

## Returns

* `result`- account addresses changed in the block

## Example

#### Request

{% tabs %}
{% tab title="Curl" %}
```bash
curl https://bsc-mainnet.nodereal.io/v1/your-api-key \
-X POST \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"jsonrpc": "2.0","id": 1,"method": "eth_getDiffAccounts","params": ["0x1167099"]}'
```
{% endtab %}
{% endtabs %}
